outputs.output_descr: The main objective of this project is to enable Timor-Leste to fulfil its commitments and obligations as required by Articles 4.1 and 12.1 of the Convention by preparing and reporting its Initial National Communication (INC).

project_descr: Preparation of Initial National Communication for UNFCCC
project_title: PIMS 2969 CC: Preparation of INC to UNFCCC
